description:
ErrorSense is a software designed to help you manage software development, increase product quality and improve customer satisfaction.
ErrorSense collects error information from your applications and allows you to quickly analyze them and determine the most problematic areas in your applications.
It allows to optimize your resources and quickly create an application, improving strategy within your development process.
ErrorSense fits greatly into any application development life cycle (SDLC) methodologies or models, including such as "the linear or waterfall model," "rapid application development (RAD)," "joint application development (JAD)," "the prototyping model," "the fountain model," "the spiral model," "build and fix," "synchronize-and-stabilize," etc. 
It is especially suitable for Agile and Kanban development.
This software is designed to support the ErrorSense service and is distributed under a license. The downloadable software is unable to provide any service itself and requires a license to run. Therefore, we advise our customers to register at www.errorsense.com and obtain the software license prior to download.
releaseNotes: This library is designed for .NET applications versions 2.0, 3.5, 4.0, and 4.5.
